title: Baker's Bleep
description:
Pablo Torre and Tony Kornheiser discuss if Baker Mayfield’s comments about the Browns hurt or help, Jeanie Buss calling Russell Westbrook the Lakers’ most “consistent” Laker and what the biggest headline from the US Open was last night.
